{"tid":1669663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 連登偽冒手足家人套料 [聲明]","createTime":"2019-10-22T16:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T04:56:15.000Z","uid":279460,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff0e949ca0ad558f8cd6a94adbfd45f38397e4f","tid":1669663,"uid":279460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"代友出po<br />\n格離post位巴打 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天水圍打樁機</strong></span></span>  出既post疑似popo拎黎套手足料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1669305/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1669305/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8MqXt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8MqXt7.jpg&h=d745b086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉述自女手足朋友: <br />\n<br />\n第一<br />\n宜加果位女手足係短頭髮, 唔係長頭髮, 所以呢張相影左<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已經有一段時間</span></strong></span>, 懷疑係popo唔知點樣搵返女手足N年前既相<br />\n <br />\n加上<br />\n親自幫女手足搵義務律師果位朋友, 已經同義務律師證實左, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">律師並沒有</span></strong></span>叫過任何人搵女手足被捕前既相關片段既<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 女手足如果無表姐, 點解突然彈個表姐出嚟咁有趣<br />\n<br />\n元朗哨兵正視聽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugttaWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugttaWY.jpg&h=433a8510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足真係一個都不能少架喇, 咪比D 19 popo拎到料阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8e8c717f98cdeaaa5358674fa404a2588c9c74d2","tid":1669663,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:44:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e459c886c40be854d2e4ff6